{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And got to Dahn, I guess it was, D-A-H-N, the name of a small town which was some 10 miles from the Siegfried Line.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we kind of bivouacked there and-- and got refurbished with ammunition and food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of us were even able to take showers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we then took off for the Maginot Line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at-- not at that time, not until we actually got into Germany did we do it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we captured some-- a dozen or so-- in that skirmish that I talked about.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were sent to the rear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sent a guard with them to-- for rear echelon units to pick them up and guard them until they were able to transfer them back to a-- a POW compound in the rear of our units.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were then-- at Dahn, got-- got our-- our ammunition, got cleaned up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were transported by truck then to cross the Rhine River at Worms, W-O-R-M-S, Worms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when we re-entered combat, which-- our first big combat then after being transported.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the other side of the Rhine River was Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Wurzburg was a heavy fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we just fought all day and all night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and we were fighting a pretty elite German Mountain Division, elements of that Mountain Division in Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- finally, we were able to-- we captured a number of Germans during that skirmish in Wurzbur.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was kind of a-- a funny situation there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wurzburg, there's a big castle or-- or stronghold fort up above the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You-- you may be familiar with Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's called a festung.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a great big wall that surrounded this fort-- fortress, and on it was 'heil Hitler' was written on this wall.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
